            <b><font size='11'>Community Guidelines</font></b>
            </p>
        <p>
            We want the Solutionreach Community to be a place to help customers find answers, share ideas and collaborate with other healthcare professionals who use patient relationship management software. Whether new to the healthcare industry or a 30-year veteran, there’s a place for you in the Solutionreach Community.  
        </p>
        <p>
