        </p>
        <p>
            <b>Respect Privacy.</b>
        </p>     
        <p>
            Do not post personal or any other information that you don’t want made public and respect the privacy of other members of the Solutionreach community.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>Stay on Topic.</b>
        </p>     
        <p>
            Comments and questions should be relevant to the topic being discussed. Keep in mind this is not a place for unsolicited personal or commercial advertising (for example, “Win a free laptop,” etc.). Let’s keep this a helpful environment, free of self-promotion and spam.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>Be you.</b>
